 946:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *  neither does it start a scanning process. The CapSense_CSDScan()
 947:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *  API must be called after initializing the widget to start scanning.
 948:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *
 949:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *  This function is called when no scanning is in progress. I.e.
 950:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *  CapSense_IsBusy() returns a non-busy status.
 951:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *
