 953:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *  given widget uses the CSD sensing method.
 954:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *
 955:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *  Calling this function directly from the application layer is not
