1172:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *  CapSense_CSDSetupWidgetExt() is not required every time before the
1173:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *  CapSense_CSDScanExt() function. If a previous scan was triggered in
1174:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *  any other way - CapSense_Scan(), CapSense_ScanAllWidgets() or
1175:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *  CapSense_RunTuner() - (see the CapSense_RunTuner() function
1176:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *  description for more details), the sensor must be preconfigured again by
1177:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *  using the CapSense_CSDSetupWidgetExt() API prior to calling the
1178:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *  CapSense_CSDScanExt() function.
1179:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_SensingCSD_LL.c **** *
